description:
Exploring Sweden's Hidden Secret: PUBLIC Access to Nature!
Ever heard of "allemansrätten"? 🇸🇪 This unique Swedish law lets ANYONE explore private land, camp freely, and forage wild berries! Watch me make some furry friends while discovering this amazing freedom to roam 🏕️ From coding to cow cuddles - life as an American software engineer in Sweden. 

#SwedishLife #SoftwareEngineer #ExpatLife
